project_descr: Multy Donor Trust Fund (MDTF): Waste Management Project: Initiated through the Aceh Emergency Response and Transitional Recovery.

outputs.output_descr: Tsunami Recovery Waste Management Project (TRWMP) was formally established in Dec. 2005, upon agreement with Multi Donor Fund.  The primary aim of this project was to provide support to district-level government in response.
